          FontWeight->"Bold"], 
        "=", \(\(1\/\@\(1 + \((\(f'\)[x])\)\^2\)\) \({1, \(f'\)[
              x]}\)\(\ \)\)}]]],
  "\n\t\nFor vectors in  ",
  Cell[BoxData[
