Cell[TextData[{
  StyleBox["A new construction of the Circle of Curvature",
    FontWeight->"Bold",
    FontColor->RGBColor[0, 0, 1]],
  "\n\n\t\tWhat determines a circle?  A center and a radius.  The formula for \
the radius of curvature is well established.  What idea could we use to help \
