"\<  The radius  = \>", 
            Rcc[H\_\(\(\[LeftDoubleBracket]\)\(i\)\(\[RightDoubleBracket]\)\)]\
];\)\ ];\)\ \), "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
    \(\(Print["\<Take the limit and get the circle of curvature\>"];\)\), "\
\[IndentingNewLine]", 
    \(\(Print["\<           The radius = \>", \[Rho][0.0]];\)\)}], "Input"],

Cell[BoxData[{
