b)\)\^2\ \ \ \  \[Equal] \ r\^2;\)\ \ \), "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
    \(\(eqn2\  = \ \ \((f[t - h] - a)\)\^2 + \((g[t - h] - b)\)\^2\  \[Equal] \
\ r\^2;\)\ \ \), "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
    \(\(eqn3\  = \ \ \((f[t + h] - a)\)\^2 + \((g[t + h] - b)\)\^2\  \[Equal] \
\ r\^2;\)\ \ \), "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
    \(\(eqns = {eqn1, eqn2, eqn3};\)\), "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
    \(\(Print[\*"\"\<Find the collocation circle (x-a\!\(\()\^2\)\) + \
